	(10534, '2013-07-03 11:43:33', 10086, 2, 3, 'eg\n\nCurrently, the filter rhythms need a structure like\n\nBabblingBrook.Filter.rhythm = {\n  init : function(){\n    // init code\n  },\n  main : function(id){\n    // main code for each offer\n  }\n};\n\nThis should be converted to an anonymous function such as \nfunction () {\n\n  var init = function () {\n\n  };\n\n  var main = function () {\n\n  };\n\n  return {\n    init : init,\n    main : main\n  };\n}', NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL, NULL),
